{"tid":2043390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際戰線下一個戰場：6月底G7峰會","createTime":"2020-05-30T11:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T12:42:54.000Z","uid":83713,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad9b37aa605ef6701d38bbdce45d036d30a615b","tid":2043390,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"節錄自 <a href=\"https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4601592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Fstory%2F8662%2F4601592&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=a1c358b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4601592</a><br />\n<br />\n川普政府在6月底，還有另一個「關鍵舞台」等待發揮&mdash;&mdash;也就是原本要辦在大衛營，但因疫情關係一度取消要改成線上會議，但上週卻又突然轉折決定改在華府實體見面的「G7領袖高峰會」。<br />\n<br />\n「G7的明確表態，對於施壓中國而言，絕對有其必要！」像是歐巴馬政府的亞太政策顧問米德羅斯（Evan Medeiros）就認為：美國當前的香港制裁對策，雖然會給美中港三方帶來相當大的經濟衝擊，但這些壓力似乎仍不足逼迫北京退讓？鑑此，能否在G7高峰會中，組織起足夠強硬的中國包圍網&mdash;&mdash;特別是重新拉攏德國、法國這些不願公開表態的騎牆派意見「遠離北京」&mdash;&mdash;必將成為至關重要的戰略關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n米德羅斯等傳統外交幕僚的意見大多認為，當前的中國，就是看準了美國受困於疫情經濟與11月大選的束縛而無法動作，並因此不斷離間對此心存疑慮的歐洲國家。因此儘管川普能大量暴走，但沒能拉攏或要求歐盟陣營的狀況，或也將使進擊的中國有恃無恐。<br />\n<br />\n儘管川普本人目前已就G7高峰會的「真人碰面」積極運作，據稱也已說服英國首相強生（Boris Johnson）&mdash;&mdash;施壓香港問題的最佳箭頭人選&mdash;&mdash;以及法國總統馬克宏（Emmanuel Macron）&mdash;&mdash;國內頗有疑慮，但對香港問題最不願發言的歐洲領袖之一&mdash;&mdash;同意赴美。<br />\n<br />\n但另一個G7巨頭人物&mdash;&mdash;德國總理梅克爾（Angela Merkel）&mdash;&mdash;目前已確認要因防疫理由而婉拒真人出席。據報，川普與梅克爾就防疫、WHO與中國問題，本週曾情緒激動地在電話中針鋒相對。而梅克爾不願對香港議題的正面表態，亦也正遭遇本國政壇的質疑。<br />\n<br />\nMerkel 雖然唔想得罪中國，但黨內開始有質疑聲音，GPhone尋日都有提到： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/3033151796777308\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fposts%2F3033151796777308&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=3568030e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/3033151796777308</a><br />\n<br />\n國際戰線有冇可能向G7其他成員施壓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d89e61fb140a978ebcb83a6440795ddc458b16","tid":2043390,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"推比文宣巴絲睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20600fcd396b6ef90aa2495ff95eaa5cd7c87202","tid":2043390,"uid":303674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53346eae9baad1299fd51d542ffa3675979848ff","tid":2043390,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f15c737e4f50be8fdacfd6d4dd1c381ad9e77ed5","tid":2043390,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"舊年g20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d88c7d5fb0efb492eaa59a925d52882ed6743c3","tid":2043390,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f15c737e4f50be8fdacfd6d4dd1c381ad9e77ed5","tid":2043390,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"舊年g20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"推到手足見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}